@*
    _ValidationScriptsPartial.cshtml
    
    Provides client-side validation scripts for forms.
    ASP.NET Core uses jQuery Validation and jQuery Validation Unobtrusive
    to enable client-side validation based on data annotations.
    
    This partial is referenced in views that use forms with validation,
    typically placed in a @section Scripts block.
*@

